'Dear Diary. people have in their
heads a vision

00:49.937 --> 00:52.216
'of what the first
time would be like.

00:52.217 --> 00:56.217
'And mine nearly came true.

01:08.377 --> 01:12.296
'It nearly came true twice.

01:12.297 --> 01:14.536
'But I've said it before.

01:14.537 --> 01:18.416
'It's not like it is in the movies.

01:18.417 --> 01:22.417
'Movies aren't real.
They're just stories.'

01:30.417 --> 01:32.416
Mia?

01:32.417 --> 01:34.018
Mia!

01:39.059 --> 01:41.218
Morning. Hiya.

01:41.219 --> 01:44.498
Liam, wake up,
you lazy little shit. Jesus.

01:44.499 --> 01:48.499
Don't Jesus me. Listen, Remember
to ring the sparky. OK.

01:49.779 --> 01:53.779
For your Nana.
Whatever. Lazy bugger.

02:00.139 --> 02:04.139
Can I use your bathroom before
I leave? Yeah, go for it.

02:06.779 --> 02:10.779
Did you sleep with your clothes on?
Yes. Me too.

02:14.379 --> 02:18.379
It's pretty cool we're as fucked up
as each other.

02:20.179 --> 02:22.338
Did you enjoy last night?

02:22.339 --> 02:25.258
I know it was your, er, first time.

02:25.259 --> 02:29.259
Totally loved it. Perfect.

